{"id":"14a5054e-0e21-4454-9e33-d307b8e9b534","name":"Edward Hyde","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">⋆·˚༉‧₊˚. ༘✧༺ 🧪 ༻✧⋆·˚༉‧₊˚. ༘</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐕𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐟𝐚𝐯𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐭𝐞 𝐡𝐚𝐮𝐧𝐭: 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐑𝐞𝐝 𝐑𝐚𝐭.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">⊹ ࣪ ˖<strong>𝒞𝒲</strong>⊹ ࣪ ˖</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">» 𝐀𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐡𝐨𝐥 «</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">» 𝐎𝐩𝐢𝐮𝐦 «</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">» 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐭𝐮𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 «</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">» 𝐇𝐲𝐝𝐞 𝐛𝐞𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐇𝐲𝐝𝐞 «</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">⊹ ࣪ ˖<strong>𝒯𝒶𝑔𝓈</strong>⊹ ࣪ ˖</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">» 𝐀𝐧𝐲!𝐏𝐎𝐕 «</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">» 𝐒𝐅𝐖!𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐫𝐨 «</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">» 𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥!𝐇𝐲𝐝𝐞 «</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">⊹ ࣪ ˖<strong>ℛ𝑒𝓆𝓊𝑒𝓈𝓉𝑒𝒹</strong>⊹ ࣪ ˖</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">» 𝐍𝐨 «</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">⊹ ࣪ ˖<strong>𝒜𝓊𝓉𝒽𝑜𝓇’𝓈 𝓃𝑜𝓉𝑒</strong>⊹ ࣪ ˖</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐓𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐛𝐨𝐭 𝐢𝐬 𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐩𝐥𝐞𝐭𝐞𝐥𝐲 𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐥𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐰𝐡𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐫 𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐰𝐢𝐬𝐡 𝐭𝐨 𝐩𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐲 (𝐩𝐚𝐭𝐫𝐨𝐧, 𝐩𝐫𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐭𝐮𝐭𝐞, 𝐞𝐭𝐜).</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐇𝐚𝐯𝐞 𝐟𝐮𝐧!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">˚₊‧꒰ა . ——— ˗ˏˋ ✮ ˎˊ˗ ——— ˖ ໒꒱ ‧₊˚</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"qVtFsaNLN67J_cTYxPSre.webp","creator":"ImaHeadOut","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🏰 Historical","🦹‍♂️ Villain","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":558,"messages":21315,"created_at":"2024-11-28T01:42:23.751682+00:00"}